OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWater firm's pollution     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fturned river black - court 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thames Water discharged large amounts  
OL,6, of waste into two rivers, killing more 
OL,7, than 1,400 fish, a court heard.        
OL,9,FThe firm released what was understood  
OL,10,Fto be "millions of litres" of undiluted
OL,11,Fsewage from treatment works near       
OL,12,FGatwick Airport in October 2017.       
OL,14,FIn February, the supplier pleaded      
OL,15,Fguilty to four charges.                
OL,17,FThe company, which serves 15 million   
OL,18,Fhouseholds, will be sentenced on       
OL,19,FTuesday as it faces concerns over its  
OL,20,Ffuture amid mounting debt.             
